{
  "stem": "14463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The school wasn't very far from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not take a bus or anything like that, I just walked up the road.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was going from 8 o'clock in the morning till 12:00, 12:30, to [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shacknoff ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shanovia. ?] This is an ordinary school, which was run by the Catholic Church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was nuns in there, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Opposite was actually a church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we always-- the Jewish boys especially, always had the problems.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A problem, because [LAUGHS] I remember as a child that-- that then-- when you saw the teacher, you have to take your hat off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, your cap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a special school cap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we couldn't take of the cap because there was a-- the-- the church was next door and had the cross, and you're not-- you're not allowed to do it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I've got some very happy memories from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one [LAUGHS] memory, which of course I cannot forget, my day-- my first day in school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was always fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, I was always running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was never walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was running, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, I-- I wasn't a child which was standing still in one-- in one place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I went to school, and my class was on the first floor in the school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I walked up-- the very first day, I think on the second lesson when there was a break, I was running in the corridor and somebody put his foot on me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I fell over, and I broke my right leg in both places.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
